      "text": "id: AutoField (PK)\nowner: FK(User, CASCADE)\n  related_name='songs'\ntitle: CharField(255)\ngenre: CharField(100)\nprompt: TextField\nvibe: CharField(100)\n  blank=True, null=True\naudio_file: FileField\n  upload_to='songs/'\ncreated_at: DateTimeField\n  auto_now_add=True\nprivacy_status: CharField\n  choices: PRIVATE | PUBLIC\n  default: PRIVATE\nshare_token: CharField(100)\n  unique, null (auto UUID\n  when status=PUBLIC)",
